# Roselira Shop

- PHP 8.2 monolith, Flowaxy framework, SQLite, no Composer
- Web root is `public/` — never expose `flowaxy/` or `storage/` directly
- Admin UI text in Ukrainian
- Minimal focused diffs; reuse existing Services/Repositories
- Do not commit `.env`, service account JSON, or database files
- Detailed docs: `.docs/` (UA), entry `README.md` (EN)

## Commit style

`fix:`, `feat:`, `refactor:`, `docs:`, `chore:` — one logical change per commit.
